<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 18:09:48 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>鲍曼惨败后，进步人士能否应对亲以色列机器？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/can-progressives-tackle-the-pro-israel-machine-after-bowmans-crushing-defeat/00000190-5530-dc65-abff-7d3b59640000</link><description>众议员贾马尔·鲍曼的盟友表示，他周二的失败不应被视为对美国人对加沙战争看法的公投，而他的批评者则表示，这表明对以色列持批评态度是一种选举责任。哪个更准确？</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 17:46:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/can-progressives-tackle-the-pro-israel-machine-after-bowmans-crushing-defeat/00000190-5530-dc65-abff-7d3b59640000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 264 天：联合国表示加沙援助人员面临的风险“无法忍受”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-264-un-says-risk-to-aid-workers-in-gaza-intolerable/00000190-555b-de50-af9b-7fffdece0000</link><description>据《华尔街日报》报道，由于内塔尼亚胡政府提出的要求减少，美国对以色列的武器运输已放缓 ■ 以色列国防部长加兰特表示，即使美国和以色列存在分歧，“我们也会闭门解决” ■ 以色列监狱管理局一直在隐瞒信息消息人士称，自战争开始以来，巴勒斯坦囚犯获得的食物数量如下： 战争进入 264 天后，您需要了解以下信息</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 16:28:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-264-un-says-risk-to-aid-workers-in-gaza-intolerable/00000190-555b-de50-af9b-7fffdece0000</guid></item><item><title>我的高中毕业生面临着以色列有史以来最黯淡的未来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-26/ty-article-opinion/.premium/my-high-school-graduates-are-facing-the-bleakest-future-israel-has-ever-known/00000190-5406-dc65-abff-7c2fb42c0000</link><description>我可以诚实地向我的学生保证国家和以色列国防军会保护他们吗？或者以色列仍将是一个民主国家？不会发生内战吗？他们在这里将过着怎样的生活？</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 15:05:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-26/ty-article-opinion/.premium/my-high-school-graduates-are-facing-the-bleakest-future-israel-has-ever-known/00000190-5406-dc65-abff-7c2fb42c0000</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，以色列减少了巴勒斯坦安全囚犯的食物，并隐瞒了数据</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-reduces-food-for-palestinian-security-prisoners-conceals-data-sources-say/00000190-542e-de5e-abd0-ff7ee9580000</link><description>自10月7日起，监狱内食物大幅减少，囚犯体重减轻，甚至挨饿。当以色列最高法院听取有关此事的请愿书时，极右翼部长本格维尔表示这是一项“威慑措施”</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 14:52:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-reduces-food-for-palestinian-security-prisoners-conceals-data-sources-say/00000190-542e-de5e-abd0-ff7ee9580000</guid></item><item><title>事实还是虚构：以色列受到全球谴责是否不公平？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/fact-or-fiction-is-israel-unfairly-singled-out-for-global-condemnation/00000190-5053-d37f-a392-7afbfbaf0000</link><description>“有偏见、预定、虚伪”：以色列的支持者这样形容国际社会在人权和国际法方面的态度。事实上，在加沙战争之前，令人震惊的是以色列所享受的长期、免费的​​旅程</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 14:33:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/fact-or-fiction-is-israel-unfairly-singled-out-for-global-condemnation/00000190-5053-d37f-a392-7afbfbaf0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列知名人士在《纽约时报》撰文敦促国会废除内塔尼亚胡的演讲</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/prominent-israelis-pen-op-ed-in-new-york-times-urging-congress-to-axe-pm-speech/00000190-5471-de50-af9b-7ffdfb730000</link><description>该报告由包括前总理巴拉克和前摩萨德负责人在内的六名以色列人共同撰写，皮尔斯敦促国会撤回内塔尼亚胡的邀请，“因为大部分以色列人对内塔尼亚胡先生的政府失去了信心”</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 14:13:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/prominent-israelis-pen-op-ed-in-new-york-times-urging-congress-to-axe-pm-speech/00000190-5471-de50-af9b-7ffdfb730000</guid></item><item><title>以色列部长赞扬法国极右党主席，打破以色列官方抵制全国集会的行为</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/minister-praises-frances-far-right-party-president-breaking-israels-official-boycott/00000190-53c3-d31c-afb9-dfd39a180000</link><description>侨民部长阿米凯·奇克利赞扬了法国极右翼全国集会主席乔丹·巴尔德拉的演讲，他在演讲中宣布两国解决方案“过时”，巴勒斯坦建国是“恐怖的奖励”。奇克利办公室：“我们与勒庞党有良好的接触”</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 11:43:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/minister-praises-frances-far-right-party-president-breaking-israels-official-boycott/00000190-53c3-d31c-afb9-dfd39a180000</guid></item><item><title>“犹太人，滚出这座城市！”：犹太儿童在伦敦涉嫌仇恨犯罪中遭到袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/get-out-of-the-city-jew-jewish-children-assaulted-in-alleged-hate-crime-in-london/00000190-5401-de5e-abd0-ff73cf470000</link><description>一群东正教男孩在中央地铁站遭到当地另一所学校的孩子们的袭击。其中一名男孩的母亲说：“他们把他的头撞到墙上，一颗牙齿脱落了。”</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 10:43:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/get-out-of-the-city-jew-jewish-children-assaulted-in-alleged-hate-crime-in-london/00000190-5401-de5e-abd0-ff73cf470000</guid></item><item><title>“黎巴嫩的战争不会是与真主党的决斗；以色列将面临伊朗的整个抵抗轴心”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-06-26/ty-article-podcast/in-a-war-with-hezbollah-israel-will-face-irans-entire-axis-of-resistance/00000190-53a1-de5e-abd0-fbf3be140000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 10:06:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-06-26/ty-article-podcast/in-a-war-with-hezbollah-israel-will-face-irans-entire-axis-of-resistance/00000190-53a1-de5e-abd0-fbf3be140000</guid></item><item><title>摇摇欲坠的内塔尼亚胡联盟改变了正统派的现状——变得更糟</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/haredim-in-no-hurry-to-exit-govt-but-top-court-ruling-widens-cracks-in-the-coalition/00000190-53c0-ddd9-a1f1-d3f286b30000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡对最高法院对草案裁决的回应具有误导性和煽动性。一些人预计他会继续宣传甘茨的“豁免法”，只是为了争取时间，因为他知道法院会否决它</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 10:00:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/haredim-in-no-hurry-to-exit-govt-but-top-court-ruling-widens-cracks-in-the-coalition/00000190-53c0-ddd9-a1f1-d3f286b30000</guid></item><item><title>两名士兵在加沙非装甲坦克爆炸中丧生后，以色列军队收紧了协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/idf-tightens-protocols-after-two-soldiers-die-in-explosion-of-non-armored-tank-in-gaza/00000190-536e-de5e-abd0-fb7e0c780000</link><description>&amp;#39;那是一个错误。消息人士称，这付出了沉重的代价，因为在调查士兵死亡事件时，以色列陆军指令下令在南部前线的每辆坦克上安装铭牌</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 09:04:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/idf-tightens-protocols-after-two-soldiers-die-in-explosion-of-non-armored-tank-in-gaza/00000190-536e-de5e-abd0-fb7e0c780000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯官员相信，只有在以色列国防军离开拉法之后，美国才会向以色列施压以达成协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/hamas-officials-believe-u-s-will-pressure-israel-for-a-deal-only-after-idf-leaves-rafah/00000190-5361-de5e-abd0-fb7383390000</link><description>一名巴勒斯坦官员表示，哈马斯领导人确信美国不会努力达成停火，而是会拖延直到加沙的激烈战斗结束。他说，以色列军队离开拉法可能是“在各方，特别是美国人放弃之前重新启动谈判的最后机会”</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 08:42:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/hamas-officials-believe-u-s-will-pressure-israel-for-a-deal-only-after-idf-leaves-rafah/00000190-5361-de5e-abd0-fb7383390000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高法院即使没有组建新政府，也可能为新的正统派犹太人铺平道路</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-may-have-paved-the-way-for-the-new-haredi-jew-if-not-a-new-government/00000190-5141-de50-af9b-7fed1c6c0000</link><description>高等法院强制征召犹太学生的裁决不会让内塔尼亚胡的联盟垮台，因为他和他的极端正统派伙伴只是想避免不可避免的情况</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 03:02:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-may-have-paved-the-way-for-the-new-haredi-jew-if-not-a-new-government/00000190-5141-de50-af9b-7fed1c6c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列负担沉重的公众感到沮丧。它不会让军方通过象征性的正统征兵而逃脱惩罚</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/israels-frustrated-public-wont-let-the-military-get-away-with-a-symbolic-haredi-draft/00000190-50e3-de50-af9b-7fef8e770000</link><description>加沙正在进行的战争凸显了以色列国防军服役人员与国家豁免人员之间的不平等有多么严重。法院的裁决为新的服役模式和替代的国民服役形式创造了机会。如果参谋长联手回避这个问题，一波愤怒可能会危及“人民军队”模式</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 03:00:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/israels-frustrated-public-wont-let-the-military-get-away-with-a-symbolic-haredi-draft/00000190-50e3-de50-af9b-7fef8e770000</guid></item><item><title>国防部长报告白宫会谈后美国向以色列的武器供应取得“重大”进展</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article-live/u-s-war-with-hezbollah-would-be-catastrophic-gallant-israel-prefers-diplomacy/00000190-524c-d37f-a392-7aee8aa30000</link><description>德国“紧急”要求公民离开黎巴嫩 ■ 内塔尼亚胡回击加兰特呼吁私下解决美以争端 ■ 报告：以色列袭击加沙北部和中部营地，以色列国防军和哈马斯在拉法的战斗加剧 ■ 从黎巴嫩发射反坦克导弹进入梅图拉，房屋遭到破坏；火箭弹落在该市后，两座建筑物起火；阿维维姆的房屋遭到反坦克导弹袭击 ■《华尔街日报》：官员称，由于以色列提出的新要求减少，美国武器运输放缓</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 02:17:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article-live/u-s-war-with-hezbollah-would-be-catastrophic-gallant-israel-prefers-diplomacy/00000190-524c-d37f-a392-7aee8aa30000</guid></item><item><title>联盟高级消息人士担心，如果以色列军队征兵法未能在七月最后期限前通过，政府就不会垮台</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/senior-coalition-sources-fear-collapse-if-conscription-law-doesnt-pass-by-july-deadline/00000190-5069-de50-af9b-7fed94820000</link><description>虽然内塔尼亚胡政府相信联盟将能够经受住周二高等法院反对极端正统军队豁免的裁决的风暴，但他们担心，如果他们提议的征兵法没有在议会获得通过，联盟可能会分崩离析</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 18:39:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/senior-coalition-sources-fear-collapse-if-conscription-law-doesnt-pass-by-july-deadline/00000190-5069-de50-af9b-7fed94820000</guid></item><item><title>最高法院对正统派法律草案的裁决令极端正统派政党陷入混乱，并使内塔尼亚胡的联盟面临风险</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/top-court-ruling-send-ultra-orthodox-parties-scrambling-puts-netanyahu-coalition-at-risk/00000190-507a-d3c0-a5d4-737a0c910000</link><description>以色列最高法院决定命令国家征召正统派人士，并停止向不合作的犹太教派提供资金，这让极端正统派政党陷入了严重的困境。虽然他们不排除解散议会的可能性，但他们明白他们没有真正的政治选择</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 18:15:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/top-court-ruling-send-ultra-orthodox-parties-scrambling-puts-netanyahu-coalition-at-risk/00000190-507a-d3c0-a5d4-737a0c910000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长命令国防机构立即招募 3,000 名极端正统派加入以色列国防军</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-orders-defense-establishment-to-immediately-recruit-3-000-ultra-orthodox/00000190-5026-d3c0-a5d4-7366941a0000</link><description>以色列高等法院一致裁定极端正统派男子有义务服兵役几个小时后，总检察长加利·巴哈拉夫-米亚拉致信国防部长和政府，表示国家必须遵守法院的裁决，并立即开始军队服役。流程草案</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 17:07:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-orders-defense-establishment-to-immediately-recruit-3-000-ultra-orthodox/00000190-5026-d3c0-a5d4-7366941a0000</guid></item><item><title>10月7日，特朗普认可了一部有关哈马斯强奸的电影。他只是忘了提及强奸事件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-25/ty-article/.highlight/trump-endorsed-a-film-about-hamas-rape-on-october-7-he-just-forgot-to-mention-the-rape/00000190-5018-d91c-abba-ff1844930000</link><description>特朗普在出人意料地呼吁观看有关哈马斯性暴力的纪录片《沉默前的尖叫》时表示，该纪录片“生动地描绘了哈马斯所造成的死亡和破坏。”这把他的主张变成了一种否认</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 16:52:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-25/ty-article/.highlight/trump-endorsed-a-film-about-hamas-rape-on-october-7-he-just-forgot-to-mention-the-rape/00000190-5018-d91c-abba-ff1844930000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 263 天：联合国停止在加沙的援助行动，直到工人得到更好的保护</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-263-un-to-halt-aid-ops-in-gaza-until-workers-are-better-protected/00000190-5019-d8cb-a19d-595b23550000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡高级助手表示不可能让哈马斯消失 ■ 哈马斯政治局主席伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚的妹妹在以色列对加沙城的袭击中丧生 ■ 据报道，巴勒斯坦总统阿巴斯将访问俄罗斯 ■ 总理内塔尼亚胡的妻子告诉人质的家人，她认为以色列国防军领导人想要上演针对她丈夫的政变 ■ 战争进入 263 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 16:23:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-263-un-to-halt-aid-ops-in-gaza-until-workers-are-better-protected/00000190-5019-d8cb-a19d-595b23550000</guid></item></channel></rss>